Case Study 3 - Patterns and Trends of Customer Behavior

DarkAstronaut

Aim

The aim of this case study is to find how a Customer acts (Purchases made by the customer) and to gain an insight on the type of the purchases made on an online platform in various countries.

Data

We use the dataset OnlineRetail.xlsx (Source: Kaggle). The data is in a Excel Workbook (XLSX) File with 8 Attributes and 541909 Observations. The attributes are:

## [1] "InvoiceNo"   "StockCode"   "Description" "Quantity"    "InvoiceDate"
## [6] "UnitPrice"   "CustomerID"  "Country"

and the sample data is:

##   InvoiceNo StockCode                         Description Quantity

## 5    536365    84029E      RED WOOLLY HOTTIE WHITE HEART.        6
## 6    536365     22752        SET 7 BABUSHKA NESTING BOXES        2
##           InvoiceDate UnitPrice CustomerID        Country
